ciscoUnityExpressMIB.name: ciscoUnityExpressMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoUnityExpressMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W. Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Phone: +1 800 553-NETS Email: cs-cue@cisco.com
ciscoUnityExpressMIB.description: The MIB Module for the management of the Cisco Unity Express (CUE) service. CUE is a voicemail service that runs in a Cisco router. CUE accepts connections from Cisco Call Manager Express (CCME), or from Cisco Call Manager (CCM). *** ABBREVIATIONS, ACRONYMS, AND SYMBOLS *** JTAPI - Java Telephony Application Programming Interface AVT - Administration Via Telephone MWI - Message Waiting Indicator AA - Auto Attendent SIP - Session Initiation Protocol AIM - Advanced Integration Module NM - Network Module

cueShutdownRequest.name: cueShutdownRequest
cueShutdownRequest.description: Shutdown all applications and halt the system.

cueAVTNumber.name: cueAVTNumber
cueAVTNumber.description: Administration Via Telephone (AVT) pilot number. AVT plays your personalized greeting when you are away and takes the message.

cueVoicemailNumber.name: cueVoicemailNumber
cueVoicemailNumber.description: Voicemail pilot number. This is used to play back your messages.

cueAANumber.name: cueAANumber
cueAANumber.description: Auto Attendant (AA) pilot number. AA is the generic voicemail entrance to the company. (If you know your party's extension...)

cueHardwareModuleType.name: cueHardwareModuleType
cueHardwareModuleType.description: Type of hardware module running this Cisco Unity Express (CUE) software. 'aim' - Advanced Integration Module (AIM). 'nm' - Network Module (NM). 'other' - This information is provided by the SNMPv2-MIB sysObjectID.

cueCallControlAgentType.name: cueCallControlAgentType
cueCallControlAgentType.description: Type of call control agent delivering calls to this voicemail application. 'ccm' - Cisco Call Manager. 'ccme' - Cisco Call Manager Express.

cueSIPGatewayIPType.name: cueSIPGatewayIPType
cueSIPGatewayIPType.description: Session Initiation Protocol (SIP) gateway IP address type.

cueSIPGatewayIP.name: cueSIPGatewayIP
cueSIPGatewayIP.description: Session Initiation Protocol (SIP) gateway IP address. The type of internet address is indicated by the value of cueSIPGatewayIPType.

cueJTAPIServerEntry.name: cueJTAPIServerEntry
cueJTAPIServerEntry.description: An entry containing information about a JTAPI Server.

cueJTAPIServerIndex.name: cueJTAPIServerIndex
cueJTAPIServerIndex.description: An arbitrary integer, a unique value for each JTAPI Server.

cueJTAPIServerName.name: cueJTAPIServerName
cueJTAPIServerName.description: Java Telephony Application Programming Interface (JTAPI) session server hostname.

cueJTAPIServerIPType.name: cueJTAPIServerIPType
cueJTAPIServerIPType.description: Java Telephony Application Programming Interface (JTAPI) session server IP address type.

cueJTAPIServerIP.name: cueJTAPIServerIP
cueJTAPIServerIP.description: Java Telephony Application Programming Interface (JTAPI) session server IP address. The type of internet address is indicated by the value of cueJTAPIServerIPType.

cueJTAPISubsystemState.name: cueJTAPISubsystemState
cueJTAPISubsystemState.description: Java Telephony Application Programming Interface (JTAPI) subsystem functional state. 'unknown' - Unknown. 'initializing' - Initializing. 'inService' - In service. 'outOfService' - Out of service. 'shuttingDown' - Shutting down. 'shutDown' - Shut down. 'partialService' - Partial service.

cueJTAPIUsername.name: cueJTAPIUsername
cueJTAPIUsername.description: Java Telephony Application Programming Interface (JTAPI) session user name.

cueJTAPISoftwareVersion.name: cueJTAPISoftwareVersion
cueJTAPISoftwareVersion.description: Java Telephony Application Programming Interface (JTAPI) software version string.

cueJTAPIPortsRegistered.name: cueJTAPIPortsRegistered
cueJTAPIPortsRegistered.description: Current number of Java Telephony Application Programming Interface (JTAPI) ports registered.

cueDefaultMailboxSize.name: cueDefaultMailboxSize
cueDefaultMailboxSize.description: Default mailbox size in seconds. New mailboxes will have this default size.

cueDefaultGreetingSize.name: cueDefaultGreetingSize
cueDefaultGreetingSize.description: Default greeting length in seconds. New mailboxes will have this default maximum greeting length.

cueDefaultMessageSizeMax.name: cueDefaultMessageSizeMax
cueDefaultMessageSizeMax.description: Default maximum message length in seconds. New mailboxes will have this default maximum single message length.

cueDefaultMessageExpiryTime.name: cueDefaultMessageExpiryTime
cueDefaultMessageExpiryTime.description: Default message age before deletion in days. New mailboxes will have this default age limit.

cueLicensedPortsMax.name: cueLicensedPortsMax
cueLicensedPortsMax.description: Maximum number of call processing ports. This is limited by the type of license purchased.

cueActiveCalls.name: cueActiveCalls
cueActiveCalls.description: Number of calls in progress. The number of active calls is limited by cueLicensedPortsMax.

cuePersonalMailboxes.name: cuePersonalMailboxes
cuePersonalMailboxes.description: Current number of personal mailboxes. A personal mailbox holds a user's voicemail messages.

cueGeneralDeliveryMailboxes.name: cueGeneralDeliveryMailboxes
cueGeneralDeliveryMailboxes.description: Current number of general delivery mailboxes. A general delivery mailbox is used to distribute a message to a list of users. Examples would be department or company wide messages via voicemail.

cueOrphanedMailboxes.name: cueOrphanedMailboxes
cueOrphanedMailboxes.description: Current number of mailboxes not associated with an owner. This may occur if the user is deleted, but the mailbox is not. The mailbox will continue to take up its defined cueAllocatedCapacity on the storage media.

cueCapacityOfVoicemail.name: cueCapacityOfVoicemail
cueCapacityOfVoicemail.description: Licensed maximum capacity of voicemail in minutes. It is the ceiling for the sum of all user's mailboxes.

cueAllocatedCapacity.name: cueAllocatedCapacity
cueAllocatedCapacity.description: Allocated capacity of voicemail in minutes. This is the sum of each user's defined mailbox size, regardless of whether they are full or empty. The cueAllocatedCapacity cannot exceed the licensed cueCapacityOfVoicemail.

cueTotalTimeUsed.name: cueTotalTimeUsed
cueTotalTimeUsed.description: Total time used in minutes for greetings and messages in all mailboxes. This cannot exceed the cueAllocatedCapacity. If all mailboxes are full, cueTotalTimeUsed will equal cueAllocatedCapacity.

cuePercentTimeUsed.name: cuePercentTimeUsed
cuePercentTimeUsed.description: Percentage of total time used for greetings and messages in all mailboxes relative to the licensed cueCapacityOfVoicemail.

cueMessageTimeUsed.name: cueMessageTimeUsed
cueMessageTimeUsed.description: Message time used in seconds. This is the total of all messages stored in all mailboxes.

cueMessageCount.name: cueMessageCount
cueMessageCount.description: Total number of messages stored in all mailboxes.

cueAverageMessageLength.name: cueAverageMessageLength
cueAverageMessageLength.description: Average message length in seconds of all messages stored in all mailboxes.

cueGreetingTimeUsed.name: cueGreetingTimeUsed
cueGreetingTimeUsed.description: Greeting time used in seconds for all greetings in all mailboxes.

cueGreetingCount.name: cueGreetingCount
cueGreetingCount.description: The number of greetings in all mailboxes.

cueMessagesLeft.name: cueMessagesLeft
cueMessagesLeft.description: Number of messages left in all mailboxes since the last boot.

cueMessagesRetrieved.name: cueMessagesRetrieved
cueMessagesRetrieved.description: Number of messages retrieved from all mailboxes since the last boot.

cueMessagesDeleted.name: cueMessagesDeleted
cueMessagesDeleted.description: Number of messages deleted from all mailboxes since the last boot.

cueLicensedMailboxesMax.name: cueLicensedMailboxesMax
cueLicensedMailboxesMax.description: Licensed maximum number of mailboxes. Enhanced licenses may be purchased to increase this limit.

cueMailboxesAbove90PercentFull.name: cueMailboxesAbove90PercentFull
cueMailboxesAbove90PercentFull.description: Number of mailboxes that are at least 90 percent full. This is an indication of general use.

cueMboxEntry.name: cueMboxEntry
cueMboxEntry.description: An entry containing information about a particular mailbox.

cueMboxIndex.name: cueMboxIndex
cueMboxIndex.description: A unique value, greater than zero, for each mailbox.

cueMboxOwner.name: cueMboxOwner
cueMboxOwner.description: The user name of the mailbox owner.

cueMboxPrimaryExtension.name: cueMboxPrimaryExtension
cueMboxPrimaryExtension.description: The phone extension number of the mailbox owner.

cueMboxType.name: cueMboxType
cueMboxType.description: The type of mailbox. A personal mailbox stores messages for a user. A general delivery mailbox distributes broadcast messages to a list of users. 'personal' - Personal mailbox of the owner. 'generalDelivery' - Assigned to a group for delivery.

cueMboxDescription.name: cueMboxDescription
cueMboxDescription.description: A textual string containing information about the mailbox.

cueMboxSize.name: cueMboxSize
cueMboxSize.description: Total number of seconds allocated for greetings and messages.

cueMboxTimeUsed.name: cueMboxTimeUsed
cueMboxTimeUsed.description: Time used for greetings and messages in seconds for this mailbox. cueMboxTimeUsed cannot exceed cueMboxSize.

cueMboxPercentTimeUsed.name: cueMboxPercentTimeUsed
cueMboxPercentTimeUsed.description: Percentage of cueMboxSize taken by greetings and messages in this mailbox.

cueMboxNumberOfMessages.name: cueMboxNumberOfMessages
cueMboxNumberOfMessages.description: Number of messages in the mailbox.

cueMboxNumberOfNewMessages.name: cueMboxNumberOfNewMessages
cueMboxNumberOfNewMessages.description: Number of new messages in the mailbox.

cueMboxNumberOfSavedMessages.name: cueMboxNumberOfSavedMessages
cueMboxNumberOfSavedMessages.description: Number of saved messages in the mailbox.

cueMboxMessageSizeMax.name: cueMboxMessageSizeMax
cueMboxMessageSizeMax.description: Maximum number of seconds for a single message.

cueMboxMessageExpiryTime.name: cueMboxMessageExpiryTime
cueMboxMessageExpiryTime.description: Message expiration time in days before a message is deleted from the mailbox.

cueMboxPlayTutorial.name: cueMboxPlayTutorial
cueMboxPlayTutorial.description: Indicates if the tutorial will be played at the next message retrieval. 'true' - The tutorial will be played at the next message retrieval. 'false' - The tutorial will not be played at the next message retrieval.

cueMboxGreetingType.name: cueMboxGreetingType
cueMboxGreetingType.description: The type of greeting played to the caller. A standard greeting uses only the owner's recorded name. A custom greeting allows the user to record the full message played to callers. 'standard' - System greeting with owner's recorded name. 'alternate' - Owner custom greeting.

cueMboxEnabled.name: cueMboxEnabled
cueMboxEnabled.description: Indicates if the mailbox is enabled for use.

cueMboxBusy.name: cueMboxBusy
cueMboxBusy.description: Indicates if the mailbox currently in use.

cueMboxMWIState.name: cueMboxMWIState
cueMboxMWIState.description: Indicates if the message waiting indicator (MWI) light on the user's phone is activated.

cueLoginAttempts.name: cueLoginAttempts
cueLoginAttempts.description: Total number of login attempts from the GUI. This includes both success and failure.

cueLoginUsernameFailures.name: cueLoginUsernameFailures
cueLoginUsernameFailures.description: Number of GUI logins rejected for unknown username.

cueLoginPasswordFailures.name: cueLoginPasswordFailures
cueLoginPasswordFailures.description: Number of GUI logins rejected for incorrect password.

cuePINAttempts.name: cuePINAttempts
cuePINAttempts.description: Total number of voicemail PIN password attempts while trying to access a mailbox. This includes successes and failures.

cuePINResets.name: cuePINResets
cuePINResets.description: Number of PIN resets, overriding a current voicemail PIN password.

cuePINUidFailures.name: cuePINUidFailures
cuePINUidFailures.description: Number of failed voicemail PIN attempts due to a bad User ID (uid) while trying to access a mailbox.

cuePINPasswordFailures.name: cuePINPasswordFailures
cuePINPasswordFailures.description: Number of failed voicemail PIN attempts due to a bad password while trying to access a mailbox.

cueNotifEnable.name: cueNotifEnable
cueNotifEnable.description: Indicates if notifications should be generated. 'true' - Notifications will be sent to targets registered via the CUE CLI. 'false' - Notifications will not be sent. Default value for this object is true because frequency of the notification generation is not very high. The following notifications are controlled by this object. - ciscoUnityExpressApplAlert - ciscoUnityExpressStorageAlert - ciscoUnityExpressSecurityAlert - ciscoUnityExpressCallMgrAlert - ciscoUnityExpressRescExhausted - ciscoUnityExpressBackupAlert - ciscoUnityExpressNTPAlert

cueNotifSeverity.name: cueNotifSeverity
cueNotifSeverity.description: The classification on the event severity. 'error' - Significant problem. 'warning' - Not immediately significant. 'informational' - Information only.

cueNotifDate.name: cueNotifDate
cueNotifDate.description: The date and time the notification occurred at the source.

cueLoginUsernameThresh.name: cueLoginUsernameThresh
cueLoginUsernameThresh.description: Notification threshold for failed login attempts due to bad user name. A notification is sent if this threshold is exceeded within a 5 minute period.

cueLoginPasswordThresh.name: cueLoginPasswordThresh
cueLoginPasswordThresh.description: Notification threshold for failed login attempts due to bad password. A notification is sent if this threshold is exceeded within a 5 minute period.

cuePINUidThresh.name: cuePINUidThresh
cuePINUidThresh.description: Notification threshold for failed PIN authentication attempts due to bad user id number. A notification is sent if this threshold is exceeded within a 5 minute period.

cuePINPasswordThresh.name: cuePINPasswordThresh
cuePINPasswordThresh.description: Notification threshold for failed PIN authentication attempts due to bad password. A notification is sent if this threshold is exceeded within a 5 minute period.

cuePINResetThresh.name: cuePINResetThresh
cuePINResetThresh.description: Notification threshold for PIN password resets. A notification is sent if this threshold is exceeded within a 5 minute period.

cueBRHistoryTable.name: cueBRHistoryTable
cueBRHistoryTable.description: A list of voicemail backup restore entries.

cueBRHistoryEntry.name: cueBRHistoryEntry
cueBRHistoryEntry.description: An entry containing information about a past voicemail backup or restore operation.

cueBRHistoryIndex.name: cueBRHistoryIndex
cueBRHistoryIndex.description: A unique value, greater than zero, for each entry.

cueBRHistoryOperation.name: cueBRHistoryOperation
cueBRHistoryOperation.description: The type of operation. 'backup' - Backup of voicemail information. 'restore' - Restore of voicemail information.

cueBRHistoryDate.name: cueBRHistoryDate
cueBRHistoryDate.description: Date and time of the operation.

cueBRHistoryResult.name: cueBRHistoryResult
cueBRHistoryResult.description: Backup or Restore operation result. 'success' - The operation was a success. 'failure' - The operation was a failure.

ciscoUnityExpressApplAlert.name: ciscoUnityExpressApplAlert
ciscoUnityExpressApplAlert.description: Notification related to applications running on Cisco Unity Express. This notification is sent when application state is changed for example changed from running to down or vice versa.

ciscoUnityExpressStorageAlert.name: ciscoUnityExpressStorageAlert
ciscoUnityExpressStorageAlert.description: Notification when storage device degradation is excessive.

ciscoUnityExpressSecurityAlert.name: ciscoUnityExpressSecurityAlert
ciscoUnityExpressSecurityAlert.description: Notification when a possible security issue is detected.

ciscoUnityExpressCallMgrAlert.name: ciscoUnityExpressCallMgrAlert
ciscoUnityExpressCallMgrAlert.description: Notification when the connection to the call manager is lost.

ciscoUnityExpressRescExhausted.name: ciscoUnityExpressRescExhausted
ciscoUnityExpressRescExhausted.description: Notification indicates that the CUE has run out of a certain specified type of resource. For example, when all JTAPI or SIP ports are in used, new incoming call can not be made, at that time this notification will be generated.

ciscoUnityExpressBackupAlert.name: ciscoUnityExpressBackupAlert
ciscoUnityExpressBackupAlert.description: Notification of a voicemail backup failure.

ciscoUnityExpressNTPAlert.name: ciscoUnityExpressNTPAlert
ciscoUnityExpressNTPAlert.description: Notification of a Network Time Protocol (NTP) error.

ciscoUnityExpressMIBCompliance.name: ciscoUnityExpressMIBCompliance
ciscoUnityExpressMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Cisco Unity Express MIB.

ciscoUnityExpressMIBComplianceRev1.name: ciscoUnityExpressMIBComplianceRev1
ciscoUnityExpressMIBComplianceRev1.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Cisco Unity Express MIB.

cueSystemGroup.name: cueSystemGroup
cueSystemGroup.description: General system parameters. It comprises of everything under cueSystem object.

cueUsageGroup.name: cueUsageGroup
cueUsageGroup.description: Voicemail usage parameters. It comprises of everything under cueUsage object.

cueSecurityGroup.name: cueSecurityGroup
cueSecurityGroup.description: Security information. It comprises of everything under cueSecurity object.

cueNotifGroup.name: cueNotifGroup
cueNotifGroup.description: Notification parameters. It comprises of everything under cueNotif object.

cueSystemGroupRev1.name: cueSystemGroupRev1
cueSystemGroupRev1.description: General system parameters. It comprises of everything under cueSystem object.
